 don't keep track of how much I spend.  It seems like every time I need money, Our guild sends a group or two to Seb for a few hours, and I masterloot.  I split when I remember, but unless someone says something about gems, I usually end up with all gemdrops for the night.  That keeps me in Peridots for a good long time.<br>
